ilities:D connid:1002 lifetime:23:14:30\n  IPSEC FLOW: permit ip 192.168.1.0/255.255.255.0 172.16.0.0/255.255.0.0\n    Active SAs: 2, origin: crypto map\n    #pkts encaps: 8200, #pkts encrypt: 8200, #pkts digest: 8200\n    #pkts decaps: 7845, #pkts decrypt: 7845, #pkts verify: 7845\n    #send errors: 0, #recv errors: 0\n    local crypto endpt.: 10.0.0.1, remote crypto endpt.: 10.2.2.2\n    path mtu 1500, ip mtu 1500, ip mtu idb Tunnel1\n    current outbound spi: 0xE5F6A7B8\n    inbound esp sas:\n      spi: 0xB8A7F6E5(3098478309)\n       transform: esp-256-aes esp-sha-hmac\n       in use settings ={Tunnel, }\n       conn id: 2003, flow_id: SW:3, sibling_flags 80000046\n    outbound esp sas:\n      spi: 0xE5F6A7B8(3858909112)\n       transform: esp-256-aes esp-sha-hmac\n       in use settings ={Tunnel, }\n       conn id: 2004, flow_id: SW:4, sibling_flags 80000046\n    inbound ah sas:\n    outbound ah sas:\n    inbound pcp sas:\n    outbound pcp sas:\n",
